    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love homemade jam in fresh homemade whole milk yogurt. It is one of my favorite breakfasts. I just finished off the last of my blueberry jam and with all of our summer rains, we never made it to the u-pick this summer. so so sad.</p>
<p>I still have peach and rhubarb and may have to look for plums! mmm.</p>
