    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My very first jam was a plum kind of thing. Owing to the fear of all that sugar mentioned above, I didn&#39;t get my set right, and the jam has to be rechristened as ice cream topping. Ever since, I&#39;ve been hesitant to go back to plums, but your jam here looks so vibrant and perfect, I&#39;ll be hoping to turn up my own stash at the market this weekend. </p>
