    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love love plum jam or Zwetschenmus as we call it in Germany. It is usually baked in the oven with much less sugar than the jam. I have seen recipe of 150 g sugar to 6 pounds of plums. I use a little more. The mus is cooked in the oven for hours until it turns thick and dark purple. </p>
