    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I planted an Italian plum tree last year, inspired by recipes I kept running across. No fruit, yet, but I&#39;ve bookmarked this recipe for the future.<br /> I may have only tasted one REAL fruit jam in my life. It was raspberry, made by a friend who picked the wild berries herself in Wyoming. I&#39;d never tasted anything like it. I had tears in my eyes. <br />Now, a back-to-earth question: Is there a way to, easily, print your recipes? I just don&#39;t see it. <br />Thank you for your blog and your books, by the way. I delight in them.</p>
